.

1. *Razloga* za to je nepoznata. (The reason for that is unknown.)
2. Oni su u potrazi za *razlogom* zašto je to postalo tako. (They are looking for a reason why it became like that.)
3. Ovi argumenti su dovoljni *razlozi* da se odlučimo za to. (These arguments are sufficient reasons to decide for that.)
4. Učinio je to bez ikakvih *razloga*. (He did it without any reasons.)
5. Oni su došli na *razlog* da promene svoje planove. (They came up with a reason to change their plans.)